件" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>读文件</span></h3><p><span>使用 </span><code>fs.readFile</code><span> 方法读文件</span></p><p><span>该方法有两个参数，第一个参数为文件的路径，第二个为回调函数，该回调函数有两回调参数，</span><code>error</code><span>和</span><code>data</code></p><p><span>当文件读取成功时</span><span>	</span><span> </span><code>error：null</code></p><p><span> </span><span>					</span><code>data：文件二进制数据</code></p><p><span>当文件读取失败时</span><span>	</span><code>error：错误对象</code></p><p><span>					</span><code>data：undefined</code><span>						</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" st