二个参数为要写入的内容，第三参数为回调函数，该回调函数有一个回调参数 </span><code>error</code></p><p><span>当文件写入成功时</span><span>		</span><code>error：null</code></p><p><span>当文件写入失败时</span><span>		</span><code>error：错误对象</code></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">fs</span>.<span class="cm-property">writeFile</span>(<span class="cm-string">'./02.2.txt'</span>,<span class="cm-string">"哈哈哈,我是node.js哦"</span>,(<span class="cm-def">error</span>) <span class="cm-operator">=&gt;</span> {</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">if</span>(<span class="cm-variable-2">error</span>){</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"文件读取失败啦！"</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;  }<span class="cm-keyword">else</span> {</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="cm-tab" role="presentation" cm-text="	">   </span><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"文件写入成功啦！"</span>); &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;  }</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">});</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 157px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 157px;"></div></div></div></pre><h2><a name="模块化" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>模块化</span></h2><h3><a name="可以所有require来引入模块" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>可以所有</span><code>require()</code><span>来引入模块</span></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>a.js:</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"a.js开始执行"</span>);</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'./b.js'</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"a.js执行完毕"</span>);</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 67px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 67px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>b.ja:</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">consloe</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"b.js开始执行"</span>);</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"b.js执行完毕"</span>);</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 45px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 45px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>当使用</span><code>require()</code><span>来引入模块时会直接执行目标模块文件。当目标模块文件执行完毕再回来继续执行当前文件。</span></p><h3><a name="获取其他模块的值" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>获取其他模块的值</span></h3><p><span>我们可以发现，无论使用下面哪一种方法都无法获取到b.js中的str。</span></p><p><span>原因是因为node中没有全局作用域，只有模块作用域。</span></p><p><span>a.js:</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//1</span></span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'./b.js'</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-variable">str</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//2</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">b</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'./b.js'</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-variable">b</span>.<span class="cm-property">str</span>);</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 157px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 157px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>b.ja:</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">str</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-string">"我是b模块的字符串"</span>;</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>每个模块中都会自动生成一个</span><code>exports</code><span>对象，该对象的内容将作为执行该模块的返回内容。</span></p><p><span>所以我们就可以所有一下方法来获取其他模块的值。</span></p><p><span>a.js:</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocap