;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>b.ja:</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">str</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-string">"我是b模块的字符串"</span>;</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">exports</span>.<span class="cm-property">str</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">str</span>;</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">exports</span>.<span class="cm-property">num</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-number">520</span>;</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 67px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 67px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>如果你想要让一个模块只返回一个值的话就不能使用一下方法</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//不能像下面的方式直接个exports赋值</span></span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">exports</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> (<span class="cm-def">x</span>,<span class="cm-def">y</span>) <span class="cm-operator">=&gt;</span> <span class="cm-variable-2">x</span> <span class="cm-operator">+</span> <span class="cm-variable-2">y</span>;</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 45px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 45px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>原因是因为每个模块中都有一个 </span><code>module</code><span> 对象，该对象有一个</span><code>exports</code><span>属性，而且系统会自动将</span><code>exports</code><span>指向 </span><code>module.exports</code><span> 中，如果直接给</span><code>exports</code><span> 赋值的话就会打断原来 </span><code>module.exports</code><span>  与 </span><code>exports</code><span> 之间的链接</span></p><p><span>只能直接修改 </span><code>module.exports</code></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">module</span>.<span class="cm-property">exports</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> (<span class="cm-def">x</span>,<span class="cm-def">y</span>) <span class="cm-operator">=&gt;</span> <span class="cm-variable-2">x</span> <span class="cm-operator">+</span> <span class="cm-variable-2">y</span>;</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>a.js:</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">b</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'./b.js'</span>);</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-variable">b</span>(<span class="cm-number">120</span>,<span class="cm-number">130</span>));</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 45px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 45px;"></div></div></div></pre><h2><a name="根据不同的请求返回不同的响应" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>根据不同的请求返回不同的响应</span></h2><h3><a name="获取客户端请求的url" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>获取客户端请求的url</span></h3><p><span>我们可以使用 </span><code>req.url</code><span> 来获取url</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; 