nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable-2">res</span>.<span class="cm-property">end</span>(<span class="cm-string">"没有找到文件"</span>)</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  }</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable-2">res</span>.<span class="cm-property">end</span>(<span class="cm-variable-2">data</span>)</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  })</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;  }</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">})</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 470px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 470px;"></div></div></div></pre><h2><a name="深入浅出node加载和导出规则" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>深入浅出node加载和导出规则</span></h2><h3><a name="加载原理" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>加载原理</span></h3><h4><a name="优先加载缓存" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>优先加载缓存</span></h4><p><span>a.js</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"正在执行a模块"</span>);</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">exports</span>.<span class="cm-property">sum</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> (<span class="cm-def">x</span>,<span class="cm-def">y</span>) <span class="cm-operator">=&gt;</span> <span class="cm-variable-2">x</span><span class="cm-operator">+</span><span class="cm-variable-2">y</span>;</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 67px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 67px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">a</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'./a'</span>)</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-variable">a</span>.<span class="cm-property">sum</span>(<span class="cm-number">1</span>,<span class="cm-number">2</span>))</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">v</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'./a'</span>)</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//输出结果为： </span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//正在执行a模块</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//3</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 134px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 134px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>我们可以发现并没有像我们预期的一样会输出两下 “正在执行a模块”，原因是 node 加载模块时会优先从缓存加载，如果缓存中没有才会去寻找指定文件</span></p><h4><a name="加载第三方模块规则" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>加载第三方模块规则</span></h4><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">template</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'art-template'</span>);</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>node 中 加载第三方模块时会优先到当前文件目录的 </span><code>node_modules</code><span> 文件夹中寻找 </span><code>art-template</code><span> 文件夹，</span></p><p><span>当寻找到时会去寻找这个文件夹中的 </span><code>package.json</code><span> 文件中寻找 </span><code>main</code><span> 属性,</span></p><p><span> 再根据 </span><code>main</code><span> 属性的 </span><code>入口模块</code><span> 文件来到当前目录寻找指定文件,当寻找到指定文件时就会加载该文件，</span></p><p><span>当没有寻找到指定文件时会寻找  </span><code>index.js</code><span> 文件,也就是说 </span><code>index,js</code><span> 是作为一个备用选项</span></p><p><span>如果以上条件都不成立，就会返回上级目录的 </span><code>node_modules</code><span> 目录查找 ，如果还没有，则继续向上一级查找。</span></p><p><span>直到查找到磁盘根目录还没有找到时抛出错误；</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><a name="packagejson包说明描述文件" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>package.json包说明/描述文件</span></h2><h3><a name="dependencies" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>dependencies</span></h3><p><span>该属性包含了当前包/项目的 </span><code>依赖</code><span> 说明文件</span></p><h3><a name="main" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>main</span></h3><p><span>该属性用于指定 </span><code>入口文件</code></p><h3><a name="创建-packagejson-文件" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>创建 package.json 文件</span></h3><p><span>该文件不需要手动文件 ， 在要创建该文件的目录下执行 </span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> init</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>会进入向导式创建</span></p><p><span>也可以使用</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> init <span class="cm-attribute">-y</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>来直接创建，使用该方式创建的文件将是默认的；</span></p><h2><a name="npm" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>npm</span></h2><p><span>网站：</span><a href='https://www.npmjs.comhttps://www.npmjs.com/'><span>npmjs.com</span></a></p><p><span>查看版本</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> <span class="cm-attribute">--version</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>升级npm</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> install <span class="cm-attribute">--global</span> <span class="cm-builtin">npm</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><h3><a name="常用命令" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>常用命令</span></h3><ul><li><p><span>npm init</span><span>			</span><span>生成 </span><code>package.json</code></p><ul><li><span>npm init -y</span><span>		</span><span>可以跳过向导快速生成  </span><code>package.json</code></li></ul></li><li><p><span>npm install</span></p><ul><li><span>一次性把 </span><code>package.json</code><span> 中的 </span><code>dependencies</code><span> 属性中的包全部安装</span></li></ul></li><li><p><span>npm install 包名</span></p><ul><li><span>安装指定包</span></li></ul></li><li><p><span>npm install --save 包名</span></p><ul><li><span>安装指定包，并将依赖信息添加到 </span><code>package.json</code><span> 中的 </span><code>dependencies</code><span> 中</span></li><li><span>npm install 包名 --save</span></li></ul></li><li><p><span>npm uninstall 包名</span></p><ul><li><span>只删除包，不删除 </span><code>package.json</code><span> 中的 </span><code>dependencies</code><span> 中的相关信息</span></li></ul></li><li><p><span>npm uninstall --sava 包名</span></p><ul><li><span>不只删除包，也删除 </span><code>package.json</code><span> 中的 </span><code>dependencies</code><span> 中的相关信息</span></li></ul></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>包名后面可以跟@版本号来指定版本，例如 </span><code>npm install --save vue-router@2.8.1</code></p><p><code>install</code><span> 可以简写为 </span><code>i</code></p><p><code>--save</code><span> 可以简写为 </span><code>-S</code><span> (大写)</span></p><h3><a name="解决npm被墙问题" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>解决npm被墙问题</span></h3><p><span>安装cnpm</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment"># 在任意目录执行都可以</span></span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment"># --global 表示全局安装</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment"># --global 不能省略</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> install <span class="cm-attribute">--global</span> cnpm</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 90px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 90px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>使用时将原来的 </span><code>npm</code><span> 换成 </span><code>cnpm</code><span> 就行啦</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>如果不想安装cnpm又想使用淘宝镜像怎么办</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> install jquery <span class="cm-attribute">--registry</span><span class="cm-operator">=</span>https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>如果想一直所有淘宝镜像又嫌输入后面的 </span><code>--registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code><span> 太麻烦怎么办？</span></p><p><span>我们可以直接配置镜像站地址</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> config <span class="cm-keyword">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment"># 执行完这条命令后，以后使用npm都将通过 https://registry.npm.taobao.org 这个地址来下载</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">#查看 npm 配置信息</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> config list</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">#切换回默认的镜像</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> config delete registry</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> config delete disturl</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 246px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 246px;"></div></div></div></pre><h3><a name="新版本" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>新版本</span></h3><p><span>在5.0以后的版本中，使用 </span><code>npm -i</code><span>  会自动创建或者更新一个 </span><code>package-lock.json</code><span> 文件，该文件相比 </span><code>package.json</code><span> 文件进行啦更大的优化，还可以锁定依赖的版本，和提高下载速度等等。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>新版本中 --save 命令是可以省略的，系统会自动添加该命令。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><a name="积累" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>积累</span></h3><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> list <span class="cm-attribute">-g</span> <span class="cm-attribute">--depth</span> <span class="cm-number">0</span><span class="cm-comment">#查看全局安过的包</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><a name="express" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>express</span></h2><h3><a name="express介绍和安装" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>express介绍和安装</span></h3><p><span>有的时候原生的 http 不足以应对开发需求，我们就需要使用框架来加快我们的开发效率。</span></p><p><span>框架能提供我们的开发效率，让我们的代码高度统一</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>在 node 中有很多web框架 在这里我们使用 </span><code>express</code></p><p><span>作者：TJ，设计出生</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>安装 express</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> install express <span class="cm-attribute">--save</span> </span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><a name="express-hello-word" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>express hello word</span></h3><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//1.加载模块</span></span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">express</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'express'</span>)</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">app</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">express</span>();</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//2处理get请求</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">app</span>.<span class="cm-property">get</span>(<span class="cm-string">'/'</span>, (<span class="cm-def">req</span>, <span class="cm-def">res</span>) <span class="cm-operator">=&gt;</span> <span class="cm-variable-2">res</span>.<span class="cm-property">send</span>(<span class="cm-string">'Hello World!'</span>))</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//3启动服务器</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">app</span>.<span class="cm-property">listen</span>(<span class="cm-number">3000</span>, () <span class="cm-operator">=&gt;</span> <span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">'Example app listening on port 3000!'</span>))</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 269px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 269px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><a name="文件修改nodemon自动重启服务" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>文件修改nodemon自动重启服务</span></h3><p><span>我们知道，每一次服务器文件经过修改都需要重新启动文件，这样会很麻烦。</span></p><p><span>我们这里可以使用一个第三方命令行工具 </span><code>nodemon</code><span> 来解决频繁修改代码重启服务器问题。</span></p><p><code>modemon</code><span> 是一个基于node.js 开发的第三方命令行工具，我们使用时需要独立安装。</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">npm</span> i <span class="cm-attribute">-g</span> nodemon</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 22px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 22px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><span>使用nodemon</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">//node</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-builtin">node</span> app.js</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">//nodemon</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">nodemon app.js</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 112px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 112px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><a name="express-处理静态资源" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>express 处理静态资源</span></h3><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><