ing-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//当以不同的方式请求同一个路径时结果会不同</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 224px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 224px;"></div></div></div></pre><h4><a name="在-express-获取表单-post请求体数据" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>在 Express 获取表单 post请求体数据</span></h4><p><span>在 Express 中没有内置的获取 POST 请求体的 API，这里我们需要使用一个第三方包： </span><code>body-parser</code></p><p><a href='http://www.expressjs.com.cn/en/resources/middleware/body-parser.html'><span>body-parser</span></a></p><p><span>安装</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="shell"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="shell"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-