"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">const</span> <span class="cm-def">Schema</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">mongoose</span>.<span class="cm-property">Schema</span>;</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">const</span> <span class="cm-def">ObjectId</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">Schema</span>.<span class="cm-property">ObjectId</span>;</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">const</span> <span class="cm-def">student</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">new</span> <span class="cm-variable">Schema</span>({<span class="cm-comment">//</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">author</span>: <span class="cm-variable">ObjectId</span>,</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">name</span>: <span class="cm-variable">String</span>,</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">age</span>: <span class="cm-variable">Number</span>,</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">sex</span>: {<span class="cm-comment">//还可以使用对象的方式指定，type代表类型，default代表默认值</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">type</span>: <span class="cm-variable">Number</span>,</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">default</span>: <span class="cm-string">"男"</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;  }</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">});</span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 269px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 269px;"></div></div></div></pre><p><strong><span>Schema可以指定的属性</span></strong></p><figure><table><thead><tr><th><span>属性</span></th><th><span>说明</span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span>type</span></td><td><span>数据类型</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>default</span></td><td><span>默认值</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>max</span></td><td><span>最大值</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>min</span></td><td><span>最小值</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>index</span></td><td><span>Boolean二级索引是否启动，true表示启动</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>lowercase</span></td><td><span>Boolean是否转换为小写，只对type为String有用</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>required</span></td><td><span>Boolean是否添加验证器</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>validate</span></td><td><span>函数 adds a </span><a href='http://www.mongoosejs.net/docs/validation.html#built-in-validators'><span>validator function</span></a><span> for this property</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>..........</span></td><td><span>更多请查看mongoose中文文档</span></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>除了在创建Schema的时候指定字段的属性以外还可以在创建成功后直接为Schema添加方法。</span></p><p><span>例如绑定方法(详情请参考官网提供的官方手册)</span></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="js" style="break-inside: unset;"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="js"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">// define a schema</span></span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">animalSchema</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">new</span> <span class="cm-variable">Schema</span>({ <span class="cm-property">name</span>: <span class="cm-variable">String</span>, <span class="cm-property">type</span>: <span class="cm-variable">String</span> });</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">// assign a function to the "methods" object of our animalSchema</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">animalSchema</span>.<span class="cm-property">methods</span>.<span class="cm-property">findSimilarTypes</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">function</span>(<span class="cm-def">cb</span>) {</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">return</span> <span class="cm-keyword">this</span>.<span class="cm-property">model</span>(<span class="cm-string">'Animal'</span>).<span class="cm-property">find</span>({ <span class="cm-property">type</span>: <span class="cm-keyword">this</span>.<span class="cm-property">type</span> }, <span class="cm-variable-2">cb</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">  };</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">Animal</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">mongoose</span>.<span class="cm-property">model</span>(<span class="cm-string">'Animal'</span>, <span class="cm-variable">animalSchema</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">dog</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">new</span> <span class="cm-variable">Animal</span>({ <span class="cm-property">type</span>: <span class="cm-string">'dog'</span> });</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">dog</span>.<span class="cm-property">findSimilarTypes</span>(<span class="cm-keyword">function</span>(<span class="cm-def">err</span>, <span class="cm-def">dogs</span>) {</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-variable-2">dogs</span>); <span class="cm-comment">// woof</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">  });</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//调用是提供具体的model的实例调用</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 403px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 403px;"></div></div></div></pre><ul><li><span>重写 mongoose 的默认方法会造成无法预料的结果，</span><a href='http://www.mongoosejs.net/docs/api.html#schema_Schema.reserved'><span>相关链接</span></a><span>。</span></li><li><strong><span>不要</span></strong><span>在自定义方法中使用 ES6 箭头函数，会造成 this 指向错误。</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><a name="设计schema-发布model" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>设计Schema 发布model</span></h3><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="js" style="break-inside: unset;"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="js"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">mongoose</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">require</span>(<span class="cm-string">'mongoose'</span>);<span class="cm-comment">//引包</span></span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">mongoose</span>.<span class="cm-property">connect</span>(<span class="cm-string">'mongodb://localhost/test'</span>);<span class="cm-comment">//连接数据库</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">db</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">mongoose</span>.<span class="cm-property">connection</span>;</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">db</span>.<span class="cm-property">on</span>(<span class="cm-string">'error'</span>, <span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">error</span>.<span class="cm-property">bind</span>(<span class="cm-variable">console</span>, <span class="cm-string">'connection error:'</span>));<span class="cm-comment">//失败</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-variable">db</span>.<span class="cm-property">once</span>(<span class="cm-string">'open'</span>, <span class="cm-keyword">function</span>() {<span class="cm-comment">//成功</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">//Mongoose 的一切始于 Schema。每个 schema 都会映射到一个 MongoDB collection</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">// ，并定义这个collection里的文档的构成。</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">Schema</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">mongoose</span>.<span class="cm-property">Schema</span>;</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">stusSchema</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">new</span> <span class="cm-variable-2">Schema</span>({<span class="cm-comment">//创建一个架构，说白了就是在设计数据库</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">name</span>:{</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">type</span>:<span class="cm-variable">String</span>,<span class="cm-comment">//数据类型</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">required</span>:<span class="cm-atom">true</span><span class="cm-comment">//true表示不能为空</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  },</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">age</span>:{</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">type</span>:<span class="cm-variable">Number</span>,</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">required</span>:<span class="cm-atom">true</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  },</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">gender</span>:{</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">type</span>:<span class="cm-variable">String</span>,</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">required</span>:<span class="cm-atom">true</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  }</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;  })</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">//为document 添加一个sing方法</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable-2">stusSchema</span>.<span class="cm-property">methods</span>.<span class="cm-property">sing</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">function</span>(){</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-string">"my name is "</span> <span class="cm-operator">+</span> <span class="cm-keyword">this</span>.<span class="cm-property">name</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;  }</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="cm-comment">//将一个架构发布为一个模型</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">//第一次参数：传入一个集合名，如果不是复数，系统会自动将大写变为小写的复数形式</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">//第二个参数：架构名</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">stus</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">mongoose</span>.<span class="cm-property">model</span>(<span class="cm-string">'stus'</span>, <span class="cm-variable-2">stusSchema</span>);<span class="cm-comment">//将一个 Schema 编译成 一个真正的模型</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">});</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 986px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 986px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><a name="静态方法" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>静态方法</span></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="javascript"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="javascript"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">animalSchema</span>.<span class="cm-property">statics</span>.<span class="cm-property">findByName</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">function</span>(<span class="cm-def">name</span>, <span class="cm-def">cb</span>) {</span></pre></div><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">return</span> <span class="cm-keyword">this</span>.<span class="cm-property">find</span>({ <span class="cm-property">name</span>: <span class="cm-keyword">new</span> <span class="cm-variable">RegExp</span>(<span class="cm-variable-2">name</span>, <span class="cm-string">'i'</span>) }, <span class="cm-variable-2">cb</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">  };</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">Animal</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-variable">mongoose</span>.<span class="cm-property">model</span>(<span class="cm-string">'Animal'</span>, <span class="cm-variable">animalSchema</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">Animal</span>.<span class="cm-property">findByName</span>(<span class="cm-string">'fido'</span>, <span class="cm-keyword">function</span>(<span class="cm-def">err</span>, <span class="cm-def">animals</span>) {</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-variable">console</span>.<span class="cm-property">log</span>(<span class="cm-variable-2">animals</span>);</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;">  });</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span class="cm-comment">//通过具体的model直接调用</span></span></pre></div></div></div></div></div><div style="position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 224px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 224px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><a name="常用增删改查api" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>常用增删改查api</span></h3><h4><a name="model方法" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>model方法 </span></h4><figure><table><thead><tr><th><span>API</span></th><th><span>说明</span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span>Model.remove(</span><query><span>,function(err))</span></td><td><span>删除符合条件的文档（数据）</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.deleteOne(</span><query><span>,function(err))</span></td><td><span>删除一条符合条件的文档（数据）</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.deleteMany(</span><query><span>,function(err))</span></td><td><span>删除所有符合条件的文档（数据）</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.find(</span><query><span>[</span><span>,</span><projection><span>]</span><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,docs))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.findOne(</span><query><span>[</span><span>,</span><projection><span>]</span><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,doc))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.findById(&lt;_id&gt;</span><span>[</span><span>,</span><projection><span>]</span><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,docs))</span></td><td><span>按_id查找</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.count(</span><query><span>,function(err, count))</span></td><td><span>统计数量</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.distinct({&quot;key1&quot;,&quot;key2&quot;,...},</span><query><span>,function(err,docs))</span></td><td><span>按key去重查询</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.where()</span></td><td><span>用于查询，用法见表格下方</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.findOneAndUpdate(</span><query><span>,</span><update><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,doc))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.findByIdAndUpdate(&lt;_id&gt;,</span><update><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,doc))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.findOneAndRemove(</span><query><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,docs))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.findByIdAndRemove(</span><query><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,doc))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.create(docs,function(err))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.insertMany(</span><docs><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,docs))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.insertOne(</span><doc><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err,doc))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.bulkWrite()</span></td><td><span>用于触发多个指令，用法见表格下方</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.replaceOne(</span><query><span>,</span><update><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err, raw))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.update(</span><query><span>,</span><update><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err, raw))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.updateMany(</span><query><span>,</span><update><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err, raw))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Model.updateOne(</span><query><span>,</span><update><span>[</span><span>,</span><option><span>]</span><span>,function(err, raw))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h4><a name="documentapi" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>documentAPI</span></h4><figure><table><thead><tr><th><span>api</span></th><th><span>说明</span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span>new Model(</span><doc><span>)</span></td><td><span>实例化一个已经注册的Model得到一个Document</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.save(function(err, product))</span></td><td><span>将Document保存到数据库中</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.remover(function(err, product))</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.set(</span><doc><span>,function(err, product))</span></td><td><doc><span>不是整个doc而是$set{}里面的{}</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.equals(doc)</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.id</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.get(key,[type])</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.set(key,value[,type])</span></td><td><span>其实还可以这样Document.key = value</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.updata(</span><update><span>[,</span><option><span>[,function(err,product)]])</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.isNew()</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.isInit(key)</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.toJSON()</span></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><span>Document.toObject()</span></td><td><span>将doc转化我普通js对象</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>除此之外还提供了很多其他的Api（例如获取当前doc的链接、model、Shema...）</span></td><td><span>官网Api文档</span></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span>Model.where()用法</span></strong></p><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="js"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="js"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presentation"><div role="presentation" style="position: relative; outline: none;"><div class="CodeMirror-measure"><pre><span>xxxxxxxxxx</span></pre></div><div class="CodeMirror-measure"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-code" role="presentation" style=""><div class="CodeMirror-activeline" style="position: relative;"><div class="CodeMirror-activeline-background CodeMirror-linebackground"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-background CodeMirror-activeline-gutter" style="left: 0px; width: 0px;"></div><pre class=" CodeMir