h: 1px; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; top: 67px;"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutters" style="display: none; height: 67px;"></div></div></div></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h1><a name="实践" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>实践</span></h1><h2><a name="node-新成员" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>node 新成员</span></h2><ul><li><span>__dirname:当前文件模块目录绝对路径</span></li><li><span>__filename:当前文件绝对路径</span></li><li><span>node中的相对路径是相对于node命令的执行目录的，所以尽量叫相对路径转化为绝对路径，这里就可以使用__dirname啦。</span></li></ul><h2><a name="mongo注意事项" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>mongo注意事项</span></h2><ul><li><span>node想获取本地数据时千万不要忘记在本地数据库名上加s，因为架构的集合名会在大写和没有复数的情况下将集合名转换为小写复数。</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><a name="node构建项目" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>node构建项目</span></h2><ul><li><span>全局安装express</span></li><li><span>全局安装 express 应用生成器 </span><code>express-generator</code></li><li><span>创建应用 </span><code>express 项目名</code></li><li><span>npm i 安装依赖</span></li><li><span>运行 www </span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><a name="jsonwebtoken" class="md-header-anchor"></a><span>JsonWebToken</span></h2><pre spellcheck="false" class="md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded" lang="js" style="break-inside: unset;"><div class="CodeMirror cm-s-inner CodeMirror-wrap" lang="js"><div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 3px; height: 0px; top: 0px; left: 8px;"><textarea autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" tabindex="0" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1em; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; height: 1em; outline: none;"></textarea></div><div class="CodeMirror-scrollbar-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-gutter-filler" cm-not-content="true"></div><div class="CodeMirror-scroll" tabindex="-1"><div class="CodeMirror-sizer" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><div style="position: relative; top: 0px;"><div class="CodeMirror-lines" role="presen